      <title>斐济前领导人拜尼马拉马在法庭判决中避免入狱</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-fiji-leader-bainimarama-avoids-jail-court-case-sentencing-2024-03-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地媒体报道，斐济长期任职的前总理弗兰克·姆拜尼马拉马本月早些时候被判犯有妨碍司法罪，并于周四被高等法院释放，避免入狱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/former-fiji-leader-bainimarama-avoids-jail-court-case-sentencing-2024-03-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 00:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚将设立 6.53 亿美元基金扩大太阳能电池板制造</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/australia-create-653-mln-fund-expand-solar-panel-manufacturing-2024-03-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞 (Anthony Albanese) 周四表示，澳大利亚将设立一项 10 亿澳元（6.53 亿美元）的基金，帮助扩大国内太阳能电池板制造，以加快从煤电向可再生能源的转型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/australia-create-653-mln-fund-expand-solar-panel-manufacturing-2024-03-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 23:15:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝中社称，俄罗斯代表团访问平壤讨论反间谍合作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-delegation-visits-pyongyang-discuss-cooperation-against-spying-kcna-says-2024-03-27/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据朝中社周四报道，俄罗斯外部情报局的一个代表团于周一至周三访问了朝鲜首都平壤，并讨论了加强反间谍合作的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-delegation-visits-pyongyang-discuss-cooperation-against-spying-kcna-says-2024-03-27/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 22:20:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
